# PAT — KSFC Attendance Tracker

Path: `~/Developer/PAT/`. Platform map: `~/Developer/STORM-PLATFORM.md`.

- Stack: Next.js 15 App Router, Prisma, Neon, JWT session (`pat_session` cookie).
- Users: staff only in v1 (`ADMIN`/`COACH`); `PLAYER` role reserved.
- Teams scoped via `UserTeamAccess`. Player names are minors' PII — no logging of full rosters.
- Planned vs actual sessions; attendance enum: YES, NO, NOT_COMMUNICATED.
